        "username": "maloo",
        "tags": [
          "SERVICE_USER"
        ]
      },
      "date": "2016-01-20 22:58:18.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests uploaded by Shadow Autotest from shadow-17vm9 for review-zfs-part-2 received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/3991720c-bfc9-11e5-9bdc-5254006e85c2). Ran 8 tests.  No failures.",
